Thoughts on this Elevator? CAD
[twinDoubleRack] [Racktest] How about a rack and pinion setup. Double helical double sided one or twin setup. The rack is double sided to eliminate deflection. And is extendable at the core you can insert a 1/2 in square tubing either aluminum or steel either tube or solid that takes most the force, Self aligning to a degree as its double helical the top and bottom gears mesh together and with the ones in front and back so you got 4 gears per double rack engaging with each double rack at a tim…

Could this be it?
